  <summary date="2021-11-18T20:14:37Z" status="Introduced in House">Renewable Energy Investment Act

This bill allows taxpayers, including certain pass-thru entities such as partnerships and S corporations, to elect to receive tax excludable payments in lieu of amounts attributable to the tax credits for energy property and for electricity produced from certain renewable resources.</summary>
